title: HIGH SCHOOL FIELD HOCKEY: Falcons top Cougars in shootout
text:
Greg VanNostrand Falcons top Cougars in shootout 
Fauquier's Lindsy Smarrelli (10) takes the ball around Kettle Run's Goalie to score the first shoot out point in Fauquier's win during Tuesday night's game. WARRENTON — It took overtime and then a shootout, but Fauquier's field hockey team extended its winning streak to four games Tuesday with a 6-4 victory.
